                <li> HTML </li>
                <li> CSS framework Twitter Bootstrap </li>
                <li> Javascript </li>
                <li> JQuery </li>
                <li> AJAX </li>
            </ul>
            <p>   This project was done basing on the materials of courses by Nikolay Tkachenko and his training center <a href="javanec.kiev.ua">Javanec.kiev.ua</a> that took place on November - December, 2012.
